title: Cross-chain Expansion
body:
Cross-chain Expansion

With the ambitious vision, there is always an irresistible temptation for us to expand the Faraland Universe beyond the limit of a specific chain. We desire to create an enormous universe where various races ARE dwelling in different kinds of lands, each one in possession of its own unique and race specific abilities and powers.

At some points in the future, building a bridge connecting different chains together in one platform is a must for the expansion. Each chain will represent its own world with distinct storylines. With limited resources and thousand years of conflicts, the Great Nation War is inevitable between these lands. All heroes from one nation will join forces to protect their territories and expand their lands. If approved, the next proposal would be about the selection of race for the new chain.

If you are interested in this idea, why don't you set the first stone on the vast Virtual Universe? 
Your vote can completely change the future.
author: 0xFF76b2dD4E24B87A084e48A7B3A9129D19483F96
